{"tid":370720,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"仙人踩場第二集 - 預告","createTime":"2017-08-23T07:36:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-24T23:24:07.000Z","uid":23479,"like":19,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"75477de02155317d877a4f4632b7f1fadb850005","tid":370720,"uid":23479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T07:36:59.000Z","msg":"第二集黎到性商店，去搵啲平時大家都想知既野，例如SM、有味底褲、少女味香水等等...<br />\n<br />\n仲會同店主一齊研究改裝性玩具<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CrR6nwgaO0o&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DCrR6nwgaO0o%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=MZbb6wOW8NUOP6KiUv6%2B8G6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=1bb7eeb5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CrR6nwgaO0o&amp;feature=youtu.be</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家仲有啲咩想問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可以係度留低問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同埋上次戰月勇者比既錢，我講左會買AV送番比大家，但好難買實體所以轉買飛機杯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，但只夠買一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecdad3c62cd177cf6cf198fe0fd1491a19ebb851","tid":370720,"uid":1515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T07:37:38.000Z","msg":"Lm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20f233437a8dca4312fddcdb828f93766776b9fd","tid":370720,"uid":23479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T08:32:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d94c4083f723483d99aa93c9a825e62bf10e9617","tid":370720,"uid":47135,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T08:33:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8